@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ / Help / Contact";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="pipboy-container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Welcome, Vault Dweller! Whether you’re a seasoned overseer or a curious newcomer, this page will help you navigate the wasteland of Vault Manager. If you can’t find the answer below, don’t hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Q: How do I create a vault?</h3>
    <p>A: To set up your very own vault, head over to the Vaults page and click "Create Vault". Fill in the details and start managing your community!</p>

    <h3>Q: How do I add or edit a dweller?</h3>
    <p>A: Navigate to the Dwellers page, then click "Add Dweller" (or choose an existing one to edit). From there, you can assign dwellers to your vaults and manage their roles.</p>

    <h3>Q: What data does Vault Manager collect?</h3>
    <p>A: Vault Manager is a demo project. We collect only minimal, non-sensitive data to help you manage your vault and dwellers. No personal data is stored without your consent.</p>

    <h3>Q: Who can I contact for support?</h3>
    <p>A: If you run into any issues or have questions about Vault Manager, please reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@vaulttec.com" style="color: var(--vault-tec-yellow);">support@vaulttec.com</a>.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you need further assistance or just want to share your vault adventures, please contact us using the information below:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@vaulttec.com" style="color: var(--vault-tec-yellow);">support@vaulttec.com</a></p>
    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>
</div>
